{"tid":2440904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"10.1荃灣 練官睇片後不斷重複形容示威者為「暴力示威人士」 協助警員更正供詞","createTime":"2021-03-10T09:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T15:18:11.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c01a8d039623d23104dddca6deefe5decec74950","tid":2440904,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"網民前年10月1日發起「六區開花」示威活動，演變成警民衝突，18歲「健仔」在荃灣中槍受傷，當日同區被捕的三男一女就暴動及縱火罪受審。庭上今播出警方及不同傳媒所拍的現場影片，<span class=\"red\">法官練錦鴻看罷片段後，不斷重覆以「暴力示威人士」稱呼現場示威者</span>。辯方大狀及後盤問警員時指出，被告並非暴力示威者，警員答：「我唔知佢係咪暴力示威者。」大狀隨即意有所指謂：「唔知，咪公道。」<br />\n<br />\n法官練錦鴻看罷片段後，<span class=\"red\">形容「大批暴力示威者以雨傘分成三層，高、中、低來掩護，向警員防線前進」。</span><br />\n<br />\n辯方指次被告僅是旁觀者，當時是見證歷史，卻不幸被捕，次被告並非示威人士。朱不同意，指次被告衣著及裝束與示威者幾乎一樣，當時穿上黑衫黑褲，戴上有粉紅色濾罐的防毒面具。此外，當時現場情況惡劣，示威者激進，未有依令離開。"},{"pid":"f47c42fa477f4be6fef1ad33298d8deb1649c1c3","tid":2440904,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:40:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/JMRBT44EOBGJFGWUIVQDTRGENY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FJMRBT44EOBGJFGWUIVQDTRGENY%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=52108852\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FJMRBT44EOBGJFGWUIVQDTRGENY%2F&h=571305e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/JMRBT44EOBGJFGWUIVQDTRGENY/</a>"},{"pid":"a15d2f61400337801d6cfdbeaed759ab3ffef62b","tid":2440904,"uid":164705,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:41:55.000Z","msg":"不如佢直接去律政司做主控官啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做法官哂左佢"},{"pid":"06be1c5caac82aa7e8fb9cfffc05a6a4f72651ed","tid":2440904,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248a8c9e59a7689f005e37cc932bf795bbef9cfc","tid":2440904,"uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a15d2f61400337801d6cfdbeaed759ab3ffef62b","tid":2440904,"uid":164705,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:41:55.000Z","msg":"不如佢直接去律政司做主控官啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做法官哂左佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"屌個主控廢撚到, 佢而家幫手做鳩被告一份<br />\n睇完片就口upup講足幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259fe32abfe5632404a059eda0f2606e3bc64e0c","tid":2440904,"uid":34811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"仲洗撚審？<br />\n有晒立場落埋場踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ceeaa421946c11d0501450c83b1bd30907808a","tid":2440904,"uid":57205,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"官=控方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29d5b761fffd28d2b455916f6f835102ee15862","tid":2440904,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:52:28.000Z","msg":"球證落埋場踢"},{"pid":"47102adaeffd9a3252186380c7942d40f1e83d8b","tid":2440904,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80a2154c2094f692064eb83f86a55f04dbe5162","tid":2440904,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"控方隨後播放片段，片中聽到有警員形容示威者是「曱甴」，而練官亦多次形容片中示威者為「暴力示威人士」。影片另拍到首被告陳在荃興徑被捕後嘗試逃走，數名警員隨即壓制他並說：「你做咩仲要逃走！」陳回答「我驚黑警，我驚共產黨」，又稱自己是急救員。"},{"pid":"09e13e25d91844c5bc8f8d891a4e2996463f89da","tid":2440904,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,